snippet.title: Forza Motorsport - New Content Trailer | Xbox @ Gamescom 2023
snippet.description: Check out the new content coming to Forza Motorsport, including a 24-hour day-night cycle, various weather conditions, and the new track Nürburgring Nordschleife, coming Spring 2024.
